            <div type="edition"><!-- transcription goes here -->
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName><name type="praenomen" key="Marcus"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan></name> <name type="gentilicium" key="Popillius">Popillius</name> <persName><name type="praenomen" key="Spurius"><expan><abbr>Sp</abbr><ex>urii</ex></expan></name></persName> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan>
                    <lb n="2"/><name type="cognomen" key="Achaicus">Achaicus</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Quietus">Quietus</name></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/>heic est conditus,
                    <lb n="4"/>mensorum <num value="11">XI</num>.
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>"Marcus Popillius Achaicus Quietus, the son of Spurius, is buried here, eleven months of age."</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary"><!-- notes go here -->
            <p>Interpuncts between all words, except at line ends. Line 3, "heic", attested archaic
                    form of "hic". Line 4, "mensorum", attested vulgar form of "mensium".</p></div>
            
